{"tid":456923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有直播] 港超聯 3/11 - 20:00 - 傑志 vs 理文","createTime":"2017-11-03T10:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T16:48:26.000Z","uid":66314,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ae326b5a6db4a9f7321acc162336316db68ab3fb","tid":456923,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"直播Link：<br />\n手機版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/mlive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fmlive%2F&d=tMGIoADtvKaCLio6ApwBwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8422af48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/mlive/</a><br />\n網頁版 <a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Flive%2F&d=tMGIoADtvKaCLio6ApwBwqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2d3f4a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/live/</a><br />\n<br />\n場地: 旺角大球場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171102/photo/bkn-20171102230924008-1102_00882_001_01b.jpg?20171102232816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171102230924008-1102_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20171102232816&h=466af2ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56ed5cffc61a49fe1d77b8a4e9347c6ea34b0b70","tid":456923,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"兩軍情報：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志</span></strong><br />\n開季至今在聯賽及盃賽均保持不敗的傑志，早前於高級組銀牌賽以5比0大勝標準流浪，上周又憑着艾力士梅開二度，加上辛祖及18歲小將史譚的入球，於菁英盃分組賽以4比0大炒香港飛馬，連續兩場大勝證明球隊火力全開上晒力。<br />\n<br />\n對於「藍鳥」上仗取得大勝，主教練朱志光認為與飛馬中堅羅斯完半場前傷出有較大關係：「每場比賽都視乎臨場發揮，上場對手有中堅受傷，直接影響咗佢哋臨場嘅穩定性。雖然金東進同保連奴已經傷愈，不過始終上半季人腳選擇較多，喺選人方面會視乎唔同情況先再作決定。」「朱Sir」又表示，希望球隊在下半季應付亞洲賽事前，輪換制度能夠步上軌道：「球隊近4至5場處理輪換方面做得唔錯，好多球員都表現出唔錯嘅比賽狀態。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">理文</span></strong><br />\n仍有兩輪賽事因颱風延期尚未舉行的理文，目前在聯賽僅踢了3場，暫時僅以1勝1和1負戰績得4分，於聯賽榜排第7位。球隊最近兩場盃賽均告輸波收場，先於高級銀牌賽不敵冠忠南區8強出局，上周則在菁英盃分組賽以1比2敗於夢想FC腳下，領隊馮嘉奇勉勵球員忘記過去：「上場菁英盃有兩位年輕球員首次落場，相比起對手嘅年輕球員恒常上陣，點都有啲影響，而且球隊上半場亦唔夠集中。不過，喺運動心理學嚟講，球員唔可以因為過去或者未來發生嘅事，影響自己依家呢一刻比賽嘅心情，我會將呢啲訊息灌輸畀佢哋。嚟緊對傑志，就只會諗對傑志，之後作客對富力會係場硬仗，但係我哋依家唔會走去諗。」"},{"pid":"d566c19f4fdbc458c1d97c62752f2e1f284800bb","tid":456923,"uid":66314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"港超積分榜<br />\n1\t<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志\t4賽10分 +9</span></strong><br />\n2\t飛馬\t4賽10分 +3<br />\n3\t南區\t5賽9分 +3<br />\n4\t大埔 5賽8分 +4<br />\n5\t夢想FC 4賽7分 -3<br />\n6\t元朗\t5賽6分 -4<br />\n7\t<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">理文\t3賽4分 0</span></strong><br />\n8\tR&amp;F富力 3賽3分 -2<br />\n9\t東方龍獅\t4賽0分 -5<br />\n10\t流浪 3賽0分 -1"},{"pid":"bc59330fe92c25d638083af61bf4bf75b38d1142","tid":456923,"uid":66314,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">傑志</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 支持<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">理文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nlike呢個留言 = 支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩隊欖炒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e7abe5e4c71eb54a5094906d7951c1941d9a48","tid":456923,"uid":66314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"裁判員:\t譚炳煥<br />\n助理裁判員1:\t周駿傑<br />\n助理裁判員2:\t盧鈺明<br />\n後備裁判員:\t黃琦海"},{"pid":"5682d47575555aac3aee08e3827a82ccec89dcd0","tid":456923,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701bc9b6496e689cc813116c1d16fe7680c45180","tid":456923,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:05: